## ðŸ“Š Contents

This repository contains 6 publication-quality figures (JPG format):

1. **fig1_bogoliubov_magnitudes.jpg** - Bogoliubov coefficient validation
2. **fig2_unitarity_delta.jpg** - Unitarity verification
3. **fig3_particle_number.jpg** - Particle number evolution
4. **fig4_ekpyrotic_tilt.jpg** - Ekpyrotic spectral tilt
5. **fig5_spectrum_properties.jpg** - Spectrum properties analysis
6. **fig6_finite_corrections.jpg** - Finite corrections validation

All figures validate analytical predictions from Loop Quantum Cosmology to < 2% accuracy for CMB-relevant modes.

